<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<span class="inline-block text-primary font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm uppercase mb-2 font-display">FAQ</span>
<h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold font-chinese text-neutral-dark mb-4">
                    常见问题解答
