<span class="material-icons-round">calendar_month</span>
</span>
<h3 class="font-chinese font-bold text-lg text-neutral-dark">如何预定您的档期？</h3>
</div>
<span class="material-icons-round text-neutral-medium group-open:rotate-180 transition-all duration-300">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 pl-[4.5rem] ml-6 mb-4 mr-6 border-t border-border-light/50">
<p class="text-neutral-medium font-chinese leading-relaxed">
                            建议您至少提前 3-6 个月进行咨询和预定，特别是在普吉岛的婚礼旺季（11月至次年4月）。您可以通过页面下方的联系方式或社交媒体与我取得联系，确认日期空档后，支付定金即可锁定档期。
                        </p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-background-light rounded-lg border border-border-light overflow-hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-primary border border-border-light">
<span class="material-icons-round">payments</span>
</span>
<h3 class="font-chinese font-bold text-lg text-neutral-dark">付款方式有哪些？</h3>
</div>
<span class="material-icons-round text-neutral-medium group-open:rotate-180 transition-all duration-300">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 pl-[4.5rem] ml-6 mb-4 mr-6 border-t border-border-light/50">
<p class="text-neutral-medium font-chinese leading-relaxed">
                            支持多种付款方式，包括微信支付 (WeChat Pay)、支付宝 (Alipay)、泰国银行转账以及 Wise 国际汇款。定金通常为总费用的 50%，余款请在服务当天或婚礼前结清。
                        </p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-background-light rounded-lg border border-border-light overflow-hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-primary border border-border-light">
<span class="material-icons-round">local_taxi</span>
</span>
<h3 class="font-chinese font-bold text-lg text-neutral-dark">是否包含上门服务和交通费？</h3>
</div>
<span class="material-icons-round text-neutral-medium group-open:rotate-180 transition-all duration-300">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 pl-[4.5rem] ml-6 mb-4 mr-6 border-t border-border-light/50">
<p class="text-neutral-medium font-chinese leading-relaxed">
                            普吉岛全岛范围内均提供上门化妆服务。对于主要海滩区域（如芭东、卡塔、卡伦、邦涛等）的酒店，交通费已包含在套餐内。如果是较偏远地区或离岛婚礼，可能会产生额外的交通补贴，具体请在咨询时确认。
                        </p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-background-light rounded-lg border border-border-light overflow-hidden">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-primary border border-border-light">
<span class="material-icons-round">brush</span>
</span>
<h3 class="font-chinese font-bold text-lg text-neutral-dark">您使用什么品牌的化妆品？</h3>
</div>
<span class="material-icons-round text-neutral-medium group-open:rotate-180 transition-all duration-300">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 pl-[4.5rem] ml-6 mb-4 mr-6 border-t border-border-light/50">
<p class="text-neutral-medium font-chinese leading-relaxed">
                            为了保证妆容的质感和持久度，我坚持使用国际一线大牌及专业彩妆产品，包括但不限于 Chanel, Dior, Tom Ford, NARS, Charlotte Tilbury, MAC, Bobbi Brown 等。如果您有特定的过敏源或产品偏好，请提前告知。
                        </p>
</div>
